messages.message: Another thought, I think we can build off the tested/currently-baking Dec 2 branch for RBS. If so, we should have no problem with a push before Jan 13. If there’s a few more changes needed for Microsoft OCR, we should be able to cherry-pick them. Afaik RBS isn’t waiting on any of the new features we’re trying to get in for Jan.
@Handsome Dave RBS takes between a day and a week to complete the deployment. Their infra person is quite savvy. We can give him a heads up that a deployment is coming up and he can plan accordingly.
